sect1.title: External Interfaces
sect1.para:
The interfaces provided by ComservCL are used by:
Sd
Cdd_SomeIP
ComservCL uses interfaces from following components:
Cdd_SomeIP
PDUI_Routing_chorus
BswM
The external interfaces are represented by the generated RTE based on the ComServ_SstSr.xml sst file. ComServ_SstSr.xml is exported from our local sst SST_ComServ.xlsx with the mapping based on ComServ_sst.xsd .
ComServ_SstSr.xml location: https://github-vni.geo.conti.de/bs-vw-meb-19-icas1-chorus/sw.sys.chorus_main_doc/blob/master/mc_sw/appl/ComServer/ComServ/Evo/cfg/rteLight/mirror/ComServ_SstSr.xml
SST_ComServ.xlsx location: https://github-vni.geo.conti.de/bs-vw-meb-19-icas1-chorus/sw.sys.chorus_main_doc/blob/master/mc_sw/appl/ComServer/ComServ/Evo/cfg/input/SST_ComServ.xlsx
ComServ_sst.xsd location: https://github-vni.geo.conti.de/bs-vw-meb-19-icas1-chorus/sw.sys.chorus_main_doc/blob/master/mc_sw/appl/ComServer/ComServ/Evo/cfg/rteCfg/xsd/ComServ_sst.xsd
